metadata.name: Crypto Floats #1
metadata.description: Tuck The Float presents 'Crypto Floats', A collection of 'Float'ible tokens brought to you by Ethereum's blockchain technology.  Crypto Floats was created to show The Float's range and education to the NFT space while bridging the gap between the analog world and the web3 aliens. 817 randomly generated digital collectibles of various rarities. With the hidden lifestyle and ready to wear gems in these NFTs (Non-'Float'ible Tokens), This niched approached was meant to fulfill the hunger of the right enthusiasts. Float no flower or companion
